{"tid":997061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"安全感 個個伴侶都需要","createTime":"2019-01-26T19:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T07:38:16.000Z","uid":140115,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a143fcdca67faaf4401ad12b1da9a3896aba8ee","tid":997061,"uid":140115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:51:33.000Z","msg":"安全感呢三隻字好似笑話 好虛假 但對伴侶黎講好重要<br />\n口講好著緊 對方好重要 呢種說話可能真係會氹到對方開心 但行動更實際<br />\n有時問下對方做緊咩 講下自己今日做咗啲咩 其實已經畀到對方好大嘅安全感<br />\n因為可以顯示到對方對你嚟講 係想分享日常生活嘅人 無論大小二事都分享就足夠<br />\n安全感係做畀伴侶 如果你係為咗對方而做嘅 對方一定會睇到<br />\n唔好將你對對方嘅愛意收埋喺心 做多少少關心對方嘅行為 表達你嘅愛意已經係一種安全感<br />\n<br />\n安全感 每個人都有需要 冇人唔需要安全感 只差在對方嘅需要大定細<br />\n雖然仲有一段時間 但預早做大家情人節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893097e42629e83e760be45c9e72ad4bb2b2baee","tid":997061,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"我個樣好安全"},{"pid":"35ac09b2f99075a424ef86a1e57aa901f8e6a2d2","tid":997061,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:52:44.000Z","msg":"ok copy that"},{"pid":"85eadb047546a720c131c8ae6ed029397c11e82a","tid":997061,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893097e42629e83e760be45c9e72ad4bb2b2baee","tid":997061,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"我個樣好安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:54:48.000Z","msg":"扮"},{"pid":"2d0b5fbf45ce0c6600cb996d8ac675f6b5cd3243","tid":997061,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85eadb047546a720c131c8ae6ed029397c11e82a","tid":997061,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893097e42629e83e760be45c9e72ad4bb2b2baee","tid":997061,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"我個樣好安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:54:48.000Z","msg":"扮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"輻射樣<img src=\"/assets/face